@next p4ng/co-design-partners-agent

! instantiated-by: Call a Synthesizer
  + context: A team needs to understand or reuse the output of a prior collaborative phase.
  + if: No member has full fluency in the previous material.
  + however: Manual parsing is slow, uneven, or error-prone.
  + then: Introduce a Synthesizer agent or role to digest, integrate, and report back the key takeaways, tensions, and open questions.
  + because: Forward motion requires shared grounding in existing work.
  + next-steps:
    - Log one concrete instance of this pattern in the futon3 ledger.
  + evidence-base:
    - Knowledge-curation roles in research projects prevent reinvention and fragmentation.
    - Systems that re-enter complex state rely on summarisation agents for reinitialisation.


